high_descs: Turn to the left, go straight, then turn to the left again to face the coffee machine at the end of the counter top.
Pick up the bread from off of the counter.
Move to the left to face the black refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, place the bread inside, close the refrigerator, wait a few seconds, open the refrigerator, pick up the bread, and close the refrigerator.
Turn to the right, walk across the kitchen, then turn to the right and face the white table in the corner.
Place the bread on the white table.
anns.task_desc: Place the refrigerated bread on top of the white table in the corner of the room.

high_descs: Walk forward, then turn left and walk over to the counter to the left of the ink.
Pick up the loaf of bread off of the counter.
Turn left and walk towards the door, then turn right to face the fridge.
Open the fridge door and put the loaf of bread inside then close the fridge door, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up and remove the load of bread, then close the fridge door.
Turn right and walk towards the wall, then hang a right and walk up to the round white table in the corner of the room.
Put the chilled loaf of bread on the white table to the right of the closest coffee mug.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled loaf of bread on the table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the loaf of bread in front of the coffee maker.
Pick up the loaf of bread from the counter.
Take a step to the left to face the fridge.
Cool the loaf of bread inside the fridge and then take it back out.
Turn right, walk past the counter, then turn left to the circle table.
Place The loaf of bread to the left of the lettuce on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled loaf of bread from the counter to the table.
